parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants are not provided with the necessary protection.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
and the vehicle's occupants may suffer injuries as a result.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected deployment of airbags can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the driver may lose control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags deploy without a crash or impact
causing a sudden and unexpected event that can distract the driver and lead to loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash, or the inadvertent deployment of airbags, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning lights on the dashboard
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
or airbags deploy without a crash or impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deterioration of wiring insulation can cause massive shorts in multiple systems, leading to engine failure, loss of critical safety features, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Engine failure at high speeds
battery drain
inoperable turn signals
brake lights
power steering
and instrument cluster (including speedometer and odometer)
bare wires shorting out wiring harnesses.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause electrical system failures, leading to engine failure, loss of critical safety features, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Engine failure at high speeds
battery drain
inoperable turn signals
brake lights
power steering
and instrument cluster (including speedometer and odometer)
bare wires shorting out wiring harnesses.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A wiring harness defect can cause a fire in the vehicle, leading to potential damage, injury, or even fatalities. The defect can also result in costly repairs and extended downtime for the vehicle.
symptoms: Wiring harness fire
burning smell
electrical system malfunctions
engine stalling
or failure to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission to shift gears properly can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Gears become stuck
difficulty shifting gears
gears slip or hesitate
vehicle hesitates or lags when shifting
unusual noises or vibrations when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure Due to Faulty Brake Master Cylinder
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause a loss of braking power, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal travels further than usual before the brakes engage
the vehicle pulls to one side while braking
the brakes make a grinding or screeching noise.
